Dialogue: 1,0:09:26.30,0:09:27.21,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,{\an8}両方パスタか
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.61,0:09:27.39,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,{\an8}都是意面啊
Dialogue: 1,0:09:27.34,0:09:28.33,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,パパうるさい
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.46,0:09:28.33,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,爸爸真是烦人
Dialogue: 1,0:09:28.38,0:09:29.22,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,ドリアないのかな
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.38,0:09:29.22,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,没有鱼贝鸡米饭吗
Dialogue: 1,0:09:29.68,0:09:30.51,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.68,0:09:30.51,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 1,0:09:30.63,0:09:31.97,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,小太郎もドリンク頼むか？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.63,0:09:31.97,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,小太郎也要饮料吗
Dialogue: 1,0:09:32.09,0:09:34.01,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,小太郎はドリンクバーね
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.09,0:09:34.01,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,小太郎要的是自助饮料
Dialogue: 1,0:09:34.14,0:09:36.31,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,母さん　ピンポン押してくれるか
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.14,0:09:36.31,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,孩子他妈  帮忙按下铃吧
Dialogue: 1,0:09:36.43,0:09:37.27,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.43,0:09:37.27,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 1,0:09:39.14,0:09:40.83,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,小太郎　聞いてる？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.14,0:09:40.83,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,小太郎  在听吗？
Dialogue: 1,0:09:41.85,0:09:43.90,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,ドリンクバー　いる
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.85,0:09:43.90,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,我要自助饮料
Dialogue: 1,0:09:45.73,0:09:47.53,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}太宰は言った
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.73,0:09:47.53,Tsuki - chs,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}太宰说过
Dialogue: 1,0:09:47.65,0:09:49.18,Tsuki - jap,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}「生きていること」
